Photo Agency Services
India News Network provides news photos to newspapers, magazines, book publishers, advertising agencies, and television channels. If you are a news publisher, you can depend on us as your one-stop source for still images.

Focus areas - Politics and Entertainment
You get the largest number of photos on politics and entertainment, including Bollywood and fashion. In addition, you will get photos of human interest, business, and sports.

More Events from Delhi and Mumbai
You will get pictures of more events from Delhi and Mumbai compred to even the biggest players in the field.

More photos per event
You will get more photos of each event, sometimes as many as 200 photos of a single event. So you have a wider base for selection. This make your photo more unique, your selection more personalised.

Free PR photos
You will get free photos released by Rashtrapati Bhawan, Press Information Bureau, government and private PR departments of organisations, and PR companies. So you do not need to source these photos independently. These photos are made available to you free of cost.

Easy search and download
You can search and browse photos by date, topic, keyword and download photos as needed. You can re-download a photo several times without any additional charge.

Pricing
Fixed Fee Plan
You can choose a fixed monthly plan for regular use. Whether you publish a daily newspaper or a magazines, fixed fee plan offers you images at a discounted rate

Pay Per Image Plan
You can sign up for Pay Per Image Plan. You can choose from variety of images available online and download only what you need.

Photo Assignments
Dedicated Photographer
You can get a dedicated news photographer in the city of your choice. The photographer will accompany your news reporters or other editorial team as and when required. The photographer will also cover a pre-specified number of assignments every month.

Event Coverage
You can ask us to shoot a planned or scheduled event for your publication. We also do event coverage for non-publication use.

Special Coverage
You can ask to shoot for special coverage such as wildlife, monuments, infrastructure, nature, people or festivals.

Technical Services
Digitisation
We scan more than ten million images every year. You can use our services to digitise your images.

Online Storage
You can get all your images online and indexed for efficient search. We use cloud-based solutions so your images are always online.

Business Services
Online Shop
Sell your images online. We will do the entire process from creating a public website, public thumbnails, private image files, password-protected customer areas where a customer can download only what is paid for and a variety of other features.

Online Syndication
You can get your images into structures that allow efficient syndication using technologies and standards currently prevalent.

Multilingual Metadata Tagging
We specialise in meta-tagging your photo archive into multiple languages. We can offer you a solution that allows to update metadata in databases and embed this data into images when needed. You can access meta-data directly from databases without need to open individual images.

IPTC Subjects and News Codes
You can get complete tagging of IPTC subjects and news codes.

